        <p>If you incorporate a generated index into your printed output<MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.FlareOnlineOnly,FlareGuides.FlareIndexingGuide,Snippets.Snippet1"> (see <MadCap:xref href="../../../Output/Printed_Output/More_About_Printed_Output/Creating_an_Index_Manually_for_Print.htm">Creating a Topic for a Print Index</MadCap:xref>)</MadCap:conditionalText>, you can customize the way the index entries look in the output. This includes adjusting properties such as font family and size, word space, space above/below, and more. You can also change the look of the entire container holding the generated index.</p>
